Author: dntlookatmepls
Text: I don’t think it’s silly at all. I regularly eat baby food.

Author: DogTeeth_Val
Text: Y'know, I had never considered baby formula but I had sorta done something similar. When I knew shit had long since hit the fan I knew I had to sort something out for myself. I didn't have as much anxiety about liquids, so I'd buy these big tubs of soy protein powder and drink them every day. I think they were the only things that had me functioning at all
